<p style="text-align:start">Dear Friends and Families,</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Thank you for your interest in Harbor House Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center, a Bane Group nursing facility. We are located in a quiet neighborhood just a short drive from the Hingham Harbor and have been a valued part of the town of Hingham since 1995.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Our 138 bed skilled nursing center has enjoyed a continued reputation for nursing excellence, providing high-level rehabilitative, medical and nursing care on a short stay or long term basis. In 2013 we introduced our Short Stay Unit, a post-hospital transitional care unit that includes programs offering orthopedic care and cardiac and pulmonary care. Harbor House is accredited by The Joint Commission.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">With over 25 years of experience as a licensed nursing home administrator, including 15 years as administrator at Harbor House, I am proud to be a part of the Bane family&rsquo;s long tradition of serving others and honored to be a part of the compassionate and skilled team of caregivers at Harbor House.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Sincerely,&nbsp;<br /> Susan Jessup&nbsp;<br /> Administrator<br /> &nbsp;</p>  <hr /> <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><u><strong>Short-Term Rehabilitation</strong></u></p>  <div class="edit_area" id="rehab-hingham-section"> <p>At Harbor House our outstanding short-term rehabilitation programs offer physical, occupational, and speech-language services. Our skilled therapists have expertise in both therapy evaluation and treatment. Services are designed to transition residents from post-acute care to home while maximizing quality of life. Our dedicated team of rehabilitation therapists, nurses, social workers, dieticians and support staff works with each patient and their family to develop a customized care plan designed to meet the patient&rsquo;s individual needs.</p>  <p><span style="color:#3399cc;">Click here</span> for our Short-term Rehabilitation brochure</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><u><strong>Short Stay Unit</strong></u></p>  <div class="edit_area" id="stay-hingham-section"> <p>At Harbor House, our Short Stay Unit offers post-hospital transitional care, providing short-term nursing and rehabilitation. Transitional care bridges the gap between the hospital setting and home, designed to help you get stronger after a hospitalization.</p>  <p>Services and programs offered on our Short Stay Unit include:</p>  <ul class="main" style="margin-left: 40px;"> 	<li>Orthopedic Program</li> 	<li>Cardiac &amp; Pulmonary Care</li> 	<li>Post-Operative Recovery Wound Care</li> 	<li>Diabetes Disease Management</li> </ul>  <p><span style="color:#3399cc;">Click here</span> for out Short Stay Unit flyer</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><u><strong>Clinical Services</strong></u></p>  <div> <ul class="main" style="margin-left: 40px;"> 	<li>IV Therapy</li> 	<li>Ostomy Care</li> 	<li>Enteral Tube Feeding</li> 	<li>Wound Care/Wound Vac</li> 	<li>Diabetic Care and Teaching</li> 	<li>Physical/Occupational/Speech and Language Therapy 7 days/week</li> 	<li>Pain Management</li> 	<li>Palliative Care and Hospice</li> 	<li>Admissions 24/7</li> </ul>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><u><strong>Individual Care</strong></u></p>  <div class="col-left"> <ul class="main" style="margin-left: 40px;"> 	<li>Stroke</li> 	<li>Hip Fracture</li> 	<li>Post-surgical Conditions</li> 	<li>Congestive Heart Failure</li> 	<li>Neurological&nbsp;diseases</li> 	<li>Multi-system disease</li> 	<li>Diabetes</li> 	<li>Pneumonia/Bronchitis/Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</li> 	<li>Cancer</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> 